{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回无情碧剑。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他双目突地一张，神色已变激昂：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子，你可曾听说过，二三十年前，武林中曾发生过一件惊天动地的大事，这件事曾令天下豪杰之士为之扼腕?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "向老师，你说的是不是那位霹雳剑展云天展大侠?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "身形毫未作势，已刷地掠出三丈开外，少年展白只觉眼前一花，这",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这年纪轻轻的少年，竟和二三十年前那霹雳剑展大侠之死有着什么关连不成?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "云公子，你可知道，当我发现这少年手中所持的剑就是当年展大侠的故物时，心里是什么滋味?云公子，我要是不将这少年得到此剑的来历问清，我怎对得起我那在九泉之下的恩人?我要是让展大侠冤沉海底，我还算是个人吗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这是找死!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扑",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "向老师，我们该走了——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老前辈可否将掌中之剑，赐还晚辈?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
