      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我又何尝知道此事竟会如此发展?我若知道'追风无影'会因此而死，那么我也万万不会取出这方丝绸来——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子，你这是干什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台亦是姓展，不知是否就是那霹雳剑展老前辈的后人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他望了华清泉倒卧着的尸身一眼，又自叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个么……小可却也不知道因何会使华老前辈如此——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台诚信君子，既然如此，小弟万无信不过兄台之理，而且此事太过离奇，亦非我等能加以妄测，只是——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追风无影",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这方绸布中，又隐藏着什么秘密呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩云神手",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要好好的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要好好的用这柄剑为我复仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "即使我知道了爹爹的仇人，又能怎样呢?我甚至连他遗留给我的剑都保存不了，我又有什么力量为他复仇?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "知了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你泄漏子老夫的秘密，老夫打死你!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我何曾泄漏过什么人的秘密，他不会是认错人了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扬手一掌，朝地上映着的影子打去，只听",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种坏东西，非打死他不可，姓展的娃娃，你说对不对?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎地知道我姓什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    }
  ],
